top 5 things to do in singapore 🇸🇬From free to expensive check them out! Might do a part 2 🤭  1. Gardens by The Bay: Pay for entry for the Cloud Forest and entry to Supertree grove but you can also watch the light show at Supertree Grove for free!  2. Marina Bay Sands Hotel: Pay to stay or pay for dinner and drinks up the top, heaps of restaurants and bars to pick from but make sure you book!  3. Chinatown: Markets, stalls, and of course Hawkers food! Enjoy looking around or you can spend your spare change 4. Raffles Hotel: Stay at the hotel or just go to the infamous bar to get a classic Singapore Sling cocktail 5. MacRitchie Resevoir: Walk the 10km loop around the beautiful lake into rainforest, with entry to the canopy bridge and lots of monkey spotting! top 5 things to do in singapore 🇸🇬From free to expensive check them out! Might do a part 2 🤭  1. Gardens by The Bay: Pay for entry for the Cloud Forest and entry to Supertree grove but you can also watch the light show at Supertree Grove for free!  2. Marina Bay Sands Hotel: Pay to stay or pay for dinner and drinks up the top, heaps of restaurants and bars to pick from but make sure you book!  3. Chinatown: Markets, stalls, and of course Hawkers food! Enjoy looking around or you can spend your spare change 4. Raffles Hotel: Stay at the hotel or just go to the infamous bar to get a classic Singapore Sling cocktail 5. MacRitchie Resevoir: Walk the 10km loop around the beautiful lake into rainforest, with entry to the canopy bridge and lots of monkey spotting!  Enjoy!  #singapore #singaporetavel #thingstodoinsingapore #cloudforest #supertreegrove #chinatown #macritchiereservoir #nature #singaporenature #marinabaysands #raffleshotel #whattodoinsingapore #travelblog #traveltips #asia #travel #marinabaysandshotel #sgtiktok
